n                \"modified_date\": \"2018-02-22 17:19:01\",\n                \"status\": \"publish\",\n                \"link\": \"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/?post_type=download&p=642632\",\n                \"content\": \"Avior is a clean and dandy free WordPress theme, designed for people, who aim for readable, photo-rich and SEO-smart writing. With Avior you\'ll easily take care of a website customization: change footer and header info like menus and social media icons, change header image, use unlimited colors to reach a perfect color scheme and more. All tweaks are easily performed visually via WordPress Customizer. A distinctive search engine optimized blog will help you stand out of the crowd and create impressive posts that will look just perfect on any modern device.\",\n                \"excerpt\": \"Avior is a clean and dandy free WordPress theme, designed for people, who aim for photo-rich and SEO-smart writing. It lets you change footer and header info like menus and social media icons, change header image, use unlimited colors to reach a perfect color scheme and more.\",\n                \"thumbnail\": \"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/02\\/avior_theme.jpg\",\n                \"category\": [\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 723,\n                        \"name\": \"Free WordPress Themes\",\n                        \"slug\": \"free-wordpress-themes\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 723,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"You found your best free WordPress themes collection - with no significant cut in functionality! Download for free a range of designs for creative and business projects.\",\n                        \"parent\": 0,\n                        \"count\": 3,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    },\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 701,\n                        \"name\": \"WordPress Themes\",\n                        \"slug\": \"wordpress-themes\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 701,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"Build a website with a premium or free WordPress theme: choose design &amp; functionality for your needs and budget.\",\n                        \"parent\": 0,\n                        \"count\": 11,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    }\n                ],\n                \"tags\": false\n            },\n            \"pricing\": {\n                \"amount\": \"0.00\"\n            },\n            \"licensing\": {\n                \"enabled\": false,\n                \"version\": \"\",\n                \"exp_unit\": \"days\",\n                \"exp_length\": \"\"\n            }\n        },\n        {\n            \"info\": {\n                \"id\": 642629,\n                \"slug\": \"timetable-event-schedule\",\n                \"title\": \"Timetable & Event Schedule\",\n                \"create_date\": \"2018-02-08 20:09:01\",\n                \"modified_date\": \"2018-02-22 17:32:31\",\n                \"status\": \"publish\",\n                \"link\": \"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/?post_type=download&p=642629\",\n                \"content\": \"<h3><img class=\\\"alignleft size-full\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/themes\\/motopress\\/images\\/timetable\\/timetable-plugin-responsive-design.png\\\" alt=\\\"responsive design\\\" \\/>Responsive Design<\\/h3>\\r\\nWordPress Timetable plugin provides your audience with a proper tablet and mobile viewing of the timetable and upcoming events widgets.\\r\\n\\r\\nIt offers you more freedom of responsive design customization implemented by two alternatives: you can set it to either standard table view or responsive modern list view for mobiles. This setting can be applied in the timetable shortcode.\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"alignright size-full\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/themes\\/motopress\\/images\\/timetable\\/timetable-plugin-shortcodes-toolkit.png\\\" alt=\\\"custom categories\\\" \\/>Toolkit of Shortcode Settings<\\/h3>\\r\\nThe toolkit doesn\\u2019t require any cross-functional or coding skills. \\r\\n\\r\\nWordPress Timetable plugin added via TinyMCE is supplied with parameters to help you maximum adjust the timetable to your needs and website design. Each setting is accompanied with sufficient clarifications to ensure you coordinate and edit your events fast without additional help. \\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"alignleft size-full\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/themes\\/motopress\\/images\\/timetable\\/full-control-of-event-parameters.png\\\" alt=\\\"various menu designs\\\" \\/>Full Control of Event Parameters<\\/h3>\\r\\nScheduling plugin for WordPress works perfectly for various classes, trainings, workshops, conferences, formal parties, concerts, non-profits, and nearly any other type of event as a set of event details for the timetable is rather universal. Using the plugin, you can edit the needed parameters your visitors expect to see while searching for the needed event: title, subtitle, time, event head, images, detailed event description, and time slots (if there are many for one event).\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"alignright size-full\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/themes\\/motopress\\/images\\/timetable\\/timetable-plugin-event-filtering.png\\\" alt=\\\"import|export menu items\\\" \\/>Easy Event Filtering <\\/h3>\\r\\nThe search results can be easily refined using the filters by events. The functionality of the plugin allows you to apply two filter styles: tabs to show all events at a time or drop-down list. The site visitors can easily filter the timetable to display the only events they are interested in. It\\u2019s very reliable in terms of navigation and guarantees the website visitors good times.\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"alignleft size-full\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/themes\\/motopress\\/images\\/timetable\\/timetable-plugin-upcoming-events.png\\\" alt=\\\"unlimited delicious images\\\" \\/>Upcoming Events<\\/h3>\\r\\nThe Upcoming events widget helps to keep the sidebar of your site clutter-free and to present all the future events in a stylish and elegant list style. It\\u2019ll duplicate design settings of the actual timetable, but will look more compact. The widget is entirely hidden when no upcoming events are scheduled. This feature increases the usability of the timetable and helps to guide the site visitors faster.\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"alignright size-full\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/themes\\/motopress\\/images\\/timetable\\/timetable-plugin-parameters-contorl.png\\\" alt=\\\"helpful widgets\\\" \\/>Powerful Schedule Functionality<\\/h3>\\r\\nEase of navigation, fast-loading events and clean design are key factors able to increase a happy user experience; a lot of shortcode options ensure that your timetable runs so and is customized the way you want. For example, you can manually adjust the row height to size the timetable according to the number of events and information output into one event cell, link particular events to external websites, and even automatically export\\/import timetable data during backup or changing hosting.\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"alignleft size-full\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/themes\\/motopress\\/images\\/timetable\\/timetable-plugin-flexible-timeframes.png\\\" alt=\\\"sell food and beverages online\\\" \\/>Flexible Timeframes<\\/h3>\\r\\nThe left \\u2018time\\u2019 column can show up to 15 minutes accurate time apart from standard hourly and half-hourly time frames. It lets you make the timetable more visually balanced and attractive depending on the amount of events and row height set within shortcode. If any unexpected delays or changes take place, your timetable can bend easily in one direction or another thanks to a couple of quick time edits in the shortcode settings.\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3><img class=\\\"alignright size-full\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/themes\\/motopress\\/images\\/timetable\\/timetable-plugin-professional-support.png\\\" alt=\\\"Integrated with MotoPress Builder\\\" \\/>Professional Support<\\/h3>\\r\\nIf you believe the timetable lacks any necessary feature, give us this good food for thought. Our professionals want to improve the plugin in terms of essential functionality and of course solve all possible problems along the way. The process starts simple, contact our support representatives and they won\\u2019t you keep waiting. The plugin is fully compatible with MotoPress <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/products\\/content-editor\\/\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">WordPress Page Builder<\\/a> and also with <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/products\\/wordpress-slider\\/\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">WordPress Slider<\\/a>.\\r\\n\\r\\n<div class=\\\"clear\\\"><\\/div>\\r\\n<p>Download <a href=\\\"\\/files\\/timetable_demo_29.08.2016.xml\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">Demo Content (xml)<\\/a><\\/p>\",\n                \"excerpt\": \"Free WordPress Event Schedule plugin will help you create a clean-looking calendar of events with custom column names, details, event head avatars and background colors. A user-friendly toolkit is provided - add your events, configure settings and your timetable is ready.\",\n                \"thumbnail\": \"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/02\\/timetable_event_schedule_plugin.png\",\n                \"category\": [\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 722,\n                        \"name\": \"Free WordPress Plugins\",\n                        \"slug\": \"free-wordpress-plugins\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 722,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"Download multipurpose and niche free WordPress plugins. Optional extra functionality for almost all plugins is available!\",\n                        \"parent\": 0,\n                        \"count\": 4,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    },\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 700,\n                        \"name\": \"WordPress Plugins\",\n                        \"slug\": \"wordpress-plugins\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 700,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"Free and premium WordPress plugins for your website. We ensure you get products created according to WordPress coding standards, niche-focused functionality and overall customization flexibility.\",\n                        \"parent\": 0,\n                        \"count\": 23,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    }\n                ],\n                \"tags\": false\n            },\n            \"pricing\": {\n                \"amount\": \"0.00\"\n            },\n            \"licensing\": {\n                \"enabled\": false,\n                \"version\": \"\",\n                \"exp_unit\": \"days\",\n                \"exp_length\": \"\"\n            }\n        },\n        {\n            \"info\": {\n                \"id\": 642627,\n                \"slug\": \"another-mailchimp-widget\",\n                \"