\",\n                \"status\": \"publish\",\n                \"link\": \"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/?post_type=download&p=223178\",\n                \"content\": \"Pricing Table is one more premium MotoPress add-on for <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/products\\/content-editor\\/\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">WordPress Visual Builder<\\/a>. Using this widget you are able to create responsive and animated pricing tables and boxes which will help you to sell your services, products, bundles and plans in an easy and awesome way.\\r\\n\\r\\nPricing tables are also highly useful for bloggers who write reviews and roundups about companies and various service providers. You can compare the main features of the products, show its pros and cons and even sell it right from your blog. All this is in a single place so visitors do not have to walk through other pages to look for additional information.\\r\\n\\r\\nMotoPress went above and beyond and made it possible to add custom content to features area using TinyMCE editor. Thus you can easily style text, add images, videos and even shortcodes creating eye-catching pricing table. \\r\\n\\r\\nAdditionally the module is completely customizable and does not require any coding skills as always. All you need is just change color with color picker or paste HTML color code to apply it for background, text, price, title, button, etc.\\r\\n\\r\\nTherefore you are able to adjust either generally style \\u2013 it would be applied by default for each new column and individual style \\u2013 edit each column with different colors. Moreover if you prefer dynamic content on your website you can enable Zoom or Slide Up animation within one click.\\r\\n\\r\\nMotoPress Pricing Table addon allows even to embed custom buy button instead of default one. That is you can use WooCommerce buttons so that your visitors could add products to the cart or paste PayPal embed code, Sign Up and other payment\\/purchase buttons. And you can definitely use shortcodes to paste your buttons with custom styles into the pricing box.\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3>Live Example #1. Random Service Plans<\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n[mpce_pta_pricing_table pta_columns=\\\"4\\\" pta_main_color=\\\"#e96656\\\" pta_bg_color=\\\"#f9f9f9\\\" pta_alternative_color=\\\"#fefefe\\\" pta_title_color=\\\"#ffffff\\\" pta_price_color=\\\"#ffffff\\\" pta_price_bg_color=\\\"#40454b\\\" pta_featur_color=\\\"#686868\\\" border=\\\"solid\\\" border_color=\\\"#eeeeee\\\" border_radius=\\\"6\\\" animation=\\\"mpce-pta-grow\\\" no_wrap=\\\"false\\\" mpce-pta-shadow=\\\"true\\\" align=\\\"mpce-pta-top\\\"]\\r\\n\\r\\n[mpce_pta_item title=\\\"Basic\\\" price_currency=\\\"$\\\" price_value=\\\"9\\\" button=\\\"link\\\" link_text=\\\"Sign Up\\\" woo_text=\\\"Buy now\\\" selected=\\\"false\\\" main_color=\\\"#1dbd3a\\\" price_bg_color=\\\"#1dbd3a\\\"]\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>1<\\/strong> User\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>5Gb<\\/strong> Disk Space\\r\\n\\r\\n<del>24\\/7 Tech Support<\\/del>\\r\\n\\r\\n<del>Email Support<\\/del>\\r\\n\\r\\nFree Upgrades\\r\\n\\r\\n[\\/mpce_pta_item]\\r\\n\\r\\n[mpce_pta_item title=\\\"Plus\\\" price_currency=\\\"$\\\" price_value=\\\"29\\\" button=\\\"link\\\" link_text=\\\"Sign Up\\\" woo_text=\\\"Buy now\\\" selected=\\\"false\\\" main_color=\\\"#1d89e4\\\" price_bg_color=\\\"#1d89e4\\\"]\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>2<\\/strong> Users\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>10Gb<\\/strong> Disk Space\\r\\n\\r\\n<del>24\\/7 Tech Support<\\/del>\\r\\n\\r\\n<del>Email Support<\\/del>\\r\\n\\r\\nFree Upgrades\\r\\n\\r\\n[\\/mpce_pta_item]\\r\\n\\r\\n[mpce_pta_item title=\\\"Pro\\\" price_currency=\\\"$\\\" price_value=\\\"59\\\" button=\\\"link\\\" link_text=\\\"Sign Up\\\" woo_text=\\\"Buy now\\\" selected=\\\"true\\\" main_color=\\\"#f67c01\\\" price_bg_color=\\\"#f67c01\\\"]\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>10<\\/strong> Users\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>50Gb<\\/strong> Disk Space\\r\\n\\r\\n24\\/7 Tech Support\\r\\n\\r\\nEmail Support\\r\\n\\r\\nFree Upgrades\\r\\n\\r\\n[\\/mpce_pta_item]\\r\\n\\r\\n[mpce_pta_