ency of payment - per month or per year, etc.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Add list of features. Using TinyMCE editor you are able to apply shortcodes or add any custom content like images, videos, etc.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Define button type among: Simple (default), WooCommerce or Script\\/HTML\\/Shortcode. Thus you are able to add code of buttons like PayPal or add your custom buttons via shortcodes.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Edit button text and URL.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>You can also make the item special and it will be zoomed a little to stand out.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>And now you can also customize table individually if you do not want to emphasize it.<\\/li>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3>Live Example #2. Bottom alignment without space<\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n[mpce_pta_pricing_table pta_columns=\\\"3\\\" pta_main_color=\\\"#43a047\\\" pta_bg_color=\\\"#455a64\\\" pta_alternative_color=\\\"#37474f\\\" pta_title_color=\\\"#ffffff\\\" pta_price_color=\\\"#ffffff\\\" pta_price_bg_color=\\\"#40454b\\\" pta_featur_color=\\\"#f2f2f2\\\" border=\\\"solid\\\" border_color=\\\"#304538\\\" border_radius=\\\"3\\\" animation=\\\"none\\\" no_wrap=\\\"true\\\" mpce-pta-shadow=\\\"true\\\" align=\\\"mpce-pta-bottom\\\"]\\r\\n\\r\\n[mpce_pta_item title=\\\"Countdown Pro\\\" subtitle=\\\"\\r\\n\\r\\n<i>MotoPress<\\/i>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\\" price_currency=\\\"$\\\" price_value=\\\"10\\\" button=\\\"script\\\" link_text=\\\"Buy now\\\" script=\\\"W3B1cmNoYXNlX2xpbmsgaWQ9IjE5MTI3NSIgc3R5bGU9ImJ0biIgY29sb3I9IiIgdGV4dD0iQWRkIHRvIENhcnQiXQ==\\\" woo_text=\\\"Buy now\\\" selected=\\\"false\\\"]\\r\\n<div style=\\\"padding: 20px;\\\">[mpce_countdown_timer date=\\\"2021-08-01 20:56:55\\\" time_zone=\\\"server_time\\\" format=\\\"HM\\\" shape_type=\\\"circle\\\" font_color=\\\"#ffffff\\\" track_color=\\\"#f9a424\\\" track_bg=\\\"#bdbdbd\\\" blocks_size=\\\"70\\\" track_width=\\\"3\\\" digits_font_size=\\\"16\\\" labels_font_size=\\\"9\\\" blocks_space=\\\"12\\\"] [\\/mpce_countdown_timer]<\\/div>\\r\\nSquare and circular styles\\r\\n\\r\\nCustom colors