ion flexibility.\",\n                        \"parent\": 0,\n                        \"count\": 23,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    }\n                ],\n                \"tags\": false\n            },\n            \"pricing\": {\n                \"amount\": \"12.00\"\n            },\n            \"licensing\": {\n                \"enabled\": true,\n                \"version\": \"1.2.1\",\n                \"exp_unit\": \"days\",\n                \"exp_length\": \"\"\n            }\n        },\n        {\n            \"info\": {\n                \"id\": 211346,\n                \"slug\": \"image-hotspot-addon\",\n                \"title\": \"Image Hotspot Addon\",\n                \"create_date\": \"2015-12-10 13:14:10\",\n                \"modified_date\": \"2018-03-26 15:27:57\",\n                \"status\": \"publish\",\n                \"link\": \"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/?post_type=download&p=211346\",\n                \"content\": \"<strong>MotoPress Image Hotspot<\\/strong> is light, easy and beneficial addon for MotoPress <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/motopress.com\\/products\\/content-editor\\/\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">WordPress Editor<\\/a> This module allows to place animated pointers with tooltips over images at your WordPress website. Use hotspot tool to create products reviews, characteristics, visual guides, instructions and recipes in easy and cheerful way. Thanks to visual text editor you can type, link and style the text right at the tooltip. Thus you are able to describe any part of the picture making it dynamic and informative. Everybody knows that illustration helps to catch and memorize information much better than static documentation. Image Hotspot converts boring page or post into into an amazing visual example which will certainly draw attention of your visitors. In order to avoid design or color conflict we took care and added color pickers for pointers, tooltips and text. Additionally there is an ability and define position of the tooltips not to cover each other if they are placed too close and make it display on hover, on click or all the time. The main point is that you can edit it visually using MotoPress Page Builder and without any coding experience at all.\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3>Live Example \\u2013 London Sightseeing Tour<\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n[mpce_image_hotspot img=\\\"218566\\\" common_hotspot_color=\\\"custom\\\" common_hotspot_custom_color=\\\"#cf000f\\\" common_plus_color=\\\"#ffffff\\\" common_hotspot_size=\\\"small\\\" common_tip_theme=\\\"custom\\\" common_custom_bg_theme=\\\"#f1f6fd\\\" common_custom_font_theme=\\\"#4183d7\\\" common_tip_position=\\\"top\\\" common_tip_show=\\\"hover\\\"]\\r\\n\\r\\n[mpce_hotspot pos_x=\\\"43\\\" pos_y=\\\"31\\\" hotspot_color=\\\"inherit\\\" hotspot_custom_color=\\\"#e25441\\\" plus_color=\\\"#ffffff\\\" hotspot_size=\\\"small\\\" tip_theme=\\\"inherit\\\" custom_bg_theme=\\\"#eb002c\\\" custom_font_theme=\\\"#ffffff\\\" tip_position=\\\"inherit\\\" tip_show=\\\"inherit\\\"]\\r\\n\\r\\nLondon Eye\\r\\n\\r\\n[\\/mpce_hotspot]\\r\\n\\r\\n[mpce_hotspot pos_x=\\\"74.5\\\" pos_y=\\\"90\\\" hotspot_color=\\\"inherit\\\" hotspot_custom_color=\\\"#e25441\\\" plus_color=\\\"#ffffff\\\" hotspot_size=\\\"big\\\" tip_theme=\\\"inherit\\\" custom_bg_theme=\\\"#eb002c\\\" custom_font_theme=\\\"#ffffff\\\" tip_position=\\\"inherit\\\" tip_show=\\\"always\\\"]\\r\\n\\r\\nSt. Paul\'s Cathedral\\r\\n\\r\\n[\\/mpce_hotspot]\\r\\n\\r\\n[mpce_hotspot pos_x=\\\"37\\\" pos_y=\\\"33\\\" hotspot_color=\\\"inherit\\\" hotspot_custom_color=\\\"#e25441\\\" plus_color=\\\"#ffffff\\\" hotspot_size=\\\"inherit\\\" tip_theme=\\\"inherit\\\" custom_bg_theme=\\\"#eb002c\\\" custom_font_theme=\\\"#ffffff\\\" tip_position=\\\"left\\\" tip_show=\\\"inherit\\\"]\\r\\n\\r\\nPalace of Westminster\\r\\n\\r\\n[\\/mpce_hotspot]\\r\\n\\r\\n[mpce_hotspot pos_x=\\\"11\\\" pos_y=\\\"53\\\" hotspot_color=\\\"inherit\\\" hotspot_custom_color=\\\"#e25441\\\" plus_color=\\\"#ff